description._content: Description: View in January, 1929, of the original lot of Terraces, (40 in number, made in October, 1921), Eastern side of the Yiallias Valley, near Kioni Forest Station, Machera Forest, middle elevation 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: January 1929 Description: Top seven terraces of a series of 40 made in October, 1921 planted December the same year. Machera Forest, Elevation about 4,000 feet, Photo 1922. Location: Cyprus Date: 1922 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
